<title id="tit" xml-lang="en-US">Using Shortcut Keys in $[officename] Impressthe "keyboard.xhp" files are only for accessibility use! Other people will complain if we ask them to press F6 for 5 times to get to a symbol bar! Except when their mouse is broken and they have to show a slide show...</title>
